
<div class="about-page">

    @{
        ViewBag.Title = "About";
    }
    <h1>@ViewBag.Title.</h1>
    <h3>How to build your own blog</h3>

    <p>To be able to create your blog you just need to do the following:</p>

    <ul>
        <li>choose the item you want to add to your blog</li>
        <li>drag it from the select box into the marked area</li>
        <li>drop it and enter the needed information</li>

    </ul>

    <img class="about-img" src="..\..\Images\about-image.png" alt="an illustration showing how to drop new elements in the future blog" />

</div>